### Get token (client credentials)
# @name auth
POST https://auth.spokayhub.top/realms/spokay-realm/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&client_id=activities-reporter&client_secret=OwwSjb2FUE6dIARyuCeFizg28BPIiyaj

> {%
client.global.set("token", response.body.access_token);
%}

###

### Create report — no token (expect 401)
POST http://localhost:8002/api/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Paris",
  "start_date": "2024-01-01",
  "end_date": "2024-01-31"
}

###

### Create report — with token (expect 202)
# @name create_report
POST http://localhost:8002/api/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "city": "Paris",
  "start_date": "2024-01-01",
  "end_date": "2024-01-31"
}

> {%
client.global.set("report_id", response.body.id);
%}

###

### Poll report status
GET http://localhost:8002/api/reports/{{report_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### MCP endpoint — no token (expect 401)
GET http://localhost:8002/mcp

###

### MCP endpoint — with token
GET http://localhost:8002/mcp
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
